(DEAN GRUNTING)

829
01:00:08,188 --> 01:00:10,439
BRUTAL: Come on, Dean.
Come on, boy, get up.

830
01:00:10,524 --> 01:00:12,358
(GASPING)
All right. Now, just breathe.

831
01:00:12,943 --> 01:00:15,069
That's it.
Just breathe. Just breathe.

832
01:00:17,030 --> 01:00:18,948
Breathe. Breathe, boy.

833
01:00:19,032 --> 01:00:20,449
DEAN: Didn't see it coming.
Come on, boy, breathe.

834
01:00:20,534 --> 01:00:22,118
DEAN: Didn't see it coming.

835
01:00:22,202 --> 01:00:24,078
Come on. Just breathe.

836
01:00:26,915 --> 01:00:28,874
We thought he was doped.

837
01:00:30,335 --> 01:00:33,713
Didn't we? Didn't we all
of us think he was doped?

838
01:00:33,797 --> 01:00:35,464
You didn't ask?

839
01:00:36,842 --> 01:00:38,634
Well, I guess
that's not a mistake...

840
01:00:39,219 --> 01:00:42,054
you'll be needing to make
again anytime soon, is it?

841
01:00:56,403 --> 01:00:59,572
You go get Dean and Harry looked at.
Make sure they're all right.

842
01:01:00,532 --> 01:01:03,409
Percy, you make the report
to the warden for me.

843
01:01:04,202 --> 01:01:05,828
Start out by saying the
situation's under control.

844
01:01:05,912 --> 01:01:06,912
It's not a story.

845
01:01:06,997 --> 01:01:09,749
He will not appreciate you
drawing out the suspense.

846
01:01:09,833 --> 01:01:12,251
Well, what about you? You're
about ready to collapse.

847
01:01:12,336 --> 01:01:15,338
Ah, I've got the Mile
till you all come back.

848
01:01:16,423 --> 01:01:17,965
Go on, now. Go.

849
01:01:23,680 --> 01:01:24,889
(GRUNTS SOFTLY)

850
01:01:26,099 --> 01:01:29,101
BRUTAL: Come on, boy.
Let's get you looked at.

851
01:01:33,774 --> 01:01:35,054
