(BREATHING HEAVILY)

852
01:01:54,836 --> 01:01:57,797
COFFEY: Boss,
I needs to see you down here.

853
01:02:01,802 --> 01:02:05,221
This is not a good time,
John Coffey...

854
01:02:05,305 --> 01:02:07,264
Not a good time at all.

855
01:02:07,349 --> 01:02:11,352
